data.description: Motivated seller, Pride of ownership shines brightly throughout this home. This 1256 SQFT 2 bedroom 1 bath home sits on a .28 acre double lot. Newly painted through out, new carpet, laminate flooring and a newly installed mini spilt w/AC to enjoy on those chilly winter days and summer nights. Enjoy your summer days on the large beautifully landscaped 700SQft deck, around the built in fire pit on the patio under a lovely gazebo. There is also a 10x20 storage shed with work bench and upper lofts for more storage with power, and a lean-to BBQ prep area with power, and if that’s wasn’t enough property also has RV graveled parking area with power, with plenty of space to build a shop if desired.
